data.title: Collectivism and Industrial Evolution / by Emile Vandervelde ; Translated by R. P. Farley
data.meta_description: 1907, English Language Edition. London : Independent Labour Party. Very good copy in the original gilt-blocked cloth. Spine bands and panel edges somewhat dust-dulled and rubbed. Minor marginalised foxing inside. Remains particularly well-preserved overall; tight, bright, clean and strong. ; 245 pages; Description: xvi, 245 p ; 19 cm. Translated from the French. Language: English ; French. Series: The Socialist library ; 5.
